text: Sión Cóhen (born 30 November 1934) is a Panamanian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle light heavyweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Panamanian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Panama Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Panama Category:Pan American Games medalists in wrestling Category:Wrestlers at the 1963 Pan American Games Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
